data.description: Don't miss this beautifully designed home in a great Lee"s Summit Location. The sellers have an assumable loan that is WELL BELOW the current mortgage rates! This large and inviting home is great for entertaining, especially in the summer when you can spend time in the beautiful in ground pool and gazebo. Step Out Back to your own private OASIS! Stunning in-ground pool and patio just waiting for you to jump in and ENJOY! MOVE RIGHT IN!!
